1. Read input array of size n
2. Compute total sum S of all elements
3. Set target = S / 2
4. Create a DP array dp[target + 1]
       dp[i] = true if subset sum i is possible
5. Initialize:
       dp[0] = true
6. For each element in array:
       Traverse DP from target to num
   Update:
       dp[j] = dp[j] OR dp[j - num]
7. Find the largest s1 ≤ target such that dp[s1] = true
8. Return result:
       minimum difference = S - 2 * s1
